================================================================================
Bundled model weights
================================================================================

The sovereign embedder ships converted weights of MiniLM-L6-v2:

  sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2
  Licensed under Apache License 2.0.
  https://huggingface.co/sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2

The original weights were converted to GS-MEM's `.sovereign` format
(models/sovereign/). The Apache-2.0 license and attribution of the upstream
model are retained.

================================================================================
Vendored crates
================================================================================

The following crates were originally developed as part of the NANTAR framework
by Galo Serrano Abad and are vendored here, relicensed under AGPL-3.0-only as
part of GS-MEM:

  - immortal-nn          (crates/immortal-nn)       — pure-Rust CPU inference
  - immortal-tokenizer   (crates/immortal-tokenizer) — WordPiece tokenizer

